r2:AccomplishmentPlannedProgram.r2:Description:
Primary objective is to ensure C2 data assets at enterprise level are visible, accessible, understandable and interoperable, by: 
1)	Leading an effective C2 Data & Services Strategy management construct to include guidance and policy recommendations;
2)	Developing and refining C2 Data Standards and Best Practices;
3)	Managing, tracking and verifying Authoritative Data Source (ADS) inventories generate utilization metrics and synchronize ADS exposure with C2 Capability development;
4)	Supporting C2 Data Pilots, Joint Capability Technology Demonstrations (JCTDs), and other Data & Service Strategy implementation activities in order to increase the warfighter's access to C2 information; and
5)	Maintaining oversight of DOD's tactical information exchange standards to ensure bi-level interoperability.
